data.description: Welcome home to your River Ridge 1st floor condo! 2Bedrooms, 2Full Bathrooms. Open floor plan with updated stainless steel appliances. Large owners' suite with private bath and walk in closet. Nice private patio with storage. Community pool, clubhouse, fitness center, walking trails. Near Uptown Westerville, Otterbein University, local businesses and restaurants,  the Polaris Fashion Mall, Easton Towne Center, and the Westerville Golf Center. Not to be missed....schedule your showing now!
